00:00:44.560 --> 00:00:47.740
very early to when they&#39;re
very, very big as a company.

00:00:47.740 --> 00:00:49.620
It&#39;s the easiest thing to say,
and

00:00:49.620 --> 00:00:50.810
the most difficult to master.

00:00:51.810 --> 00:00:56.774
And, the concept in musical
form, whoops, pardon me,

00:00:56.774 --> 00:00:58.210
very sensitive.

00:01:00.643 --> 00:01:04.100
But musical form.

00:01:04.100 --> 00:01:12.070
This is from Sly And The
