Sometimes I&#39;m right.

00:01:18.261 --> 00:01:18.761
&gt;&gt; So.

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:23.597
No difference what group I&#39;m
in.

00:01:29.141 --> 00:01:33.310
So that&#39;s, that&#39;s the musical
version of today&#39;s lesson.

00:01:33.310 --> 00:01:35.300
For those of you, you are
