00:02:33.130 --> 00:02:35.260
which is a very emotional
thing.

00:02:35.260 --> 00:02:38.680
Then raises, which is also an
emotional thing.

00:02:38.680 --> 00:02:41.390
Then we&#39;re going to evaluate
one of Sams blog posts.

